spec_data.Name: nodejs-caller-path
spec_data.Description:
Get the path of the caller module. You can't use module.parent as modules are
cached and it will return the first caller module, not necessarily the current
one.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 02:05:22 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Get the path of the caller module
